parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "AJCC M Stage M1":
  ( ["Procedure, Performed": "Tumor Staging"] Proc
    where exists ( Proc.components component1
        where component1.code in "M Category"
          and ( component1.result in "M Stage M1"
              or component1.result in "M Stage M1a"
              or component1.result in "M Stage M1b"
              or component1.result in "M Stage M1c"
          )
    ) ) MCategory
    with "Cancer Dx" Dx
      such that MCategory.relevantPeriod starts after start of Dx.prevalencePeriod

define "AJCC Stage IV":
  ( ["Procedure, Performed": "Tumor Staging"] Proc
    where exists ( Proc.components component1
        where component1.code in "TNM Stage Group"
          and ( component1.result in "Cancer Stage IV"
              or component1.result in "Cancer Stage IVA"
              or component1.result in "Cancer Stage IVB"
              or component1.result in "Cancer Stage IVC"
          )
    ) ) StageIV
    with "Cancer Dx" Dx
      such that StageIV.relevantPeriod starts after start of Dx.prevalencePeriod

define "Cancer Dx":
  First((["Diagnosis": "Cancer"] Dx
      where Dx.prevalencePeriod starts during "Measurement Period")DD
      sort by start of prevalencePeriod
  )

define "Denominator Exclusions":
  exists "Leukemia Dx"
    or exists "Testicular Cancer Dx"
    or exists "Hodgkins Disease Dx"
    or exists "Neoplasm of Placenta Dx"
    or exists "Non Hodgkins Lymphoma Dx"

define "GCSF Administered":
  ( ["Medication, Administered": "Granulocyte Colony Stimulating Factor"]
    union ["Medication, Order": "Granulocyte Colony Stimulating Factor"] ) GCSF
    with "Cancer Dx" FirstDx
      such that GCSF.relevantPeriod starts after start of FirstDx.prevalencePeriod

define "Hodgkins Disease Dx":
  ["Diagnosis": "Hodgkins Disease"] Dx
    where Dx.prevalencePeriod starts during "Measurement Period"

define "Leukemia Dx":
  ["Diagnosis": "Leukemia"] Dx
    where Dx.prevalencePeriod starts during "Measurement Period"

define "Metastatic Cancer Dx":
  ( ["Diagnosis": "Metastatic Cancer"] Metastasis
      with "Cancer Dx" Dx
        such that Metastasis.prevalencePeriod starts same day or after start of Dx.prevalencePeriod
      sort by start of prevalencePeriod
  )

define "Neoplasm of Placenta Dx":
  ["Diagnosis": "Neoplasm of Placenta"] Dx
    where Dx.prevalencePeriod starts during "Measurement Period"

define "Non Hodgkins Lymphoma Dx":
  ["Diagnosis": "Non Hodgkins Lymphoma"] Dx
    where Dx.prevalencePeriod starts during "Measurement Period"

define "Office Visits":
  ( ["Encounter, Performed": "Office Visit"]
    union ["Encounter, Performed": "Patient Provider Interaction"] ) Encounter
    where Encounter.relevantPeriod starts during "Measurement Period"

define "SDE Ethnicity":
  ["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
  ["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
  ["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
  ["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Testicular Cancer Dx":
  ["Diagnosis": "Testicular Cancer"] Dx
    where Dx.prevalencePeriod starts during "Measurement Period"

define "Numerator":
  exists "GCSF Administered"

define "Patient Age":
  AgeInYearsAt(start of "Measurement Period")>= 18

define "Initial Population":
  "Patient Age"
    and "Cancer Dx" is not null
    and Count("Office Visits")>= 2

define "Denominator":
  "Initial Population"
    and exists "Chemo Therapy"
    and ( exists "AJCC M Stage M1"
        or exists "AJCC Stage IV"
        or exists "Metastatic Cancer Dx"
    )

define "Chemo Therapy":
  ["Medication, Administered": "Anti Neoplastic Agents"] ChemoAdmin
    with "Cancer Dx" Dx
      such that ChemoAdmin.relevantPeriod starts same day or after start of Dx.prevalencePeriod
